Group
-----
Group means a role or permission category for users.

Example 1:
Group name: Developers
Purpose: Users in this group can fix bugs, update bug status, and add comments.
Users: gokula, smith

Example 2:
Group name: Testers
Purpose: Users in this group can report bugs, test fixes, and add comments.
Users: tester1

Example 3:
Group name: Project Managers
Purpose: Users in this group can create projects, assign bugs, and close completed bugs.
Users: manager1

Example 4:
Group name: Admin Team
Purpose: Users in this group can manage projects, bugs, comments, users, and groups.
Users: gokula


Simple Meaning
--------------
Project = Which app/system the bug belongs to
Bug = The actual issue
Comment = Discussion or update about the bug
User = Person using the system
Group = Role or permission category for users
